✨ Features
   🗓️ Daily Scheduled Automation – Runs automatically every day at a fixed time using n8n Schedule Trigger.
   🤖 AI-Powered Content Generation – Uses Google Gemini to generate engaging LinkedIn posts about historical events.
   💼 LinkedIn Auto Posting – Automatically publishes posts to your LinkedIn profile or company page.
   🧠 Professional Prompt Engineering – Generates posts with hooks, explanations, hashtags, and engagement questions.
   
🏗️ Workflow Overview
    *Schedule Trigger – Runs daily at a specific time.
    *Gemini AI Chain – Finds a historical fact and generates LinkedIn content.
    *LinkedIn Node – Publishes the generated post automatically.
   
🛠️ Tech Stack
    *n8n (Workflow Automation)
    *Google Gemini API (AI Content Generation)
    *LinkedIn API (Auto Posting)
    *JavaScript / JSON Workflow Configuration

🎯 Use Cases
    *Personal LinkedIn branding
    *AI content automation
    *Social media marketing
    *Educational history content
    *Portfolio AI project
